'''''This Is a Long Drive for Someone with Nothing to Think About''''' is the first proper full-length album by the [[indie rock]] band [[Modest Mouse]].

The album was released on [[Up Records]] on [[April 16]] [[1996]], on both [[Compact Disc]] and [[vinyl record|vinyl LP]]. The vinyl LP release contains two extra tracks.

