*Vinyl bonus tracks: "Edit the Sad Parts" (from the "[[Interstate 8 (album)|Interstate 8 EP]]") and "A Manic Depressive Named Laughing Boy".
*"Novocain Stain", "Beach Side Property" and "Tundra/Desert" later appeared on ''[[Interstate 8 (album)|Interstate 8 EP]]'', the first two tracks being in their demo form, while Tundra/Desert remained as the studio version
